    "attributes": {
        "action": "Change Tier 3 rules to allow pubs and restaurants to stay open",
        "additional_details": "The pub trade was struggling even before covid. This year pubs and restaurants have been one of the most affected sectors. The month of December can relate to up to 25% of a pubs annual takings alone. They need our help and support to survive. The necessary steps CAN be taken to make pubs and restaurants safe.",
        "background": "Allow pubs and restaurants to stay open in Tier 3. They must follow social distancing rules of the tier (no mixing of households etc) but will be allowed to allow customers to eat and drink inside the premises.",
